HEADWORD: Shoreless
<hw>Shore"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no shore or coast; of
indefinite or unlimited extent; <as>as, a <ex>shoreless</ex>
ocean</as>.</def> <rj><au>Young.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

